{"tid":1890871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓亞航空入寒冬 高層含總裁全請辭退3成薪、員工放無薪假","createTime":"2020-02-21T12:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T13:11:28.000Z","uid":75656,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e9d2742bf00ecb322931cd5d1592a9d5a3fa3f","tid":1890871,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕去年日韓貿易戰降低訪日旅行需求，加上近來中國武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，南韓航空公司韓亞航空（Aliana Airlines）面臨經營危機，為改善公司財務狀況，宣布包括執行長在內，全體主管請辭、全數員工放10天無薪假。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，韓亞航空2019年淨虧損從前一年的962億韓元擴大至6726億韓元；運營虧損從前一年的350億韓元擴大至3682億韓元，虧損的其中一大原因為受日韓貿易戰影響，南韓人自發抵制前往日本旅行。<br />\n<br />\n加上近來中國疫情嚴峻，旅遊需求大幅降低，韓亞航空暫時停止飛往中國26條航線中的12條，韓亞航空在最新聲明中指出，為改善公司的財務狀況，全體高層主管包含執行長，將辭去職務，並將削減年薪20%至40%。<br />\n<br />\n此外，自今日起，約有10500名員工放10天無薪假，其他員工則以不影響航班的方式，加入無薪假行列，來減低支出成本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3073121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3073121&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=2560c9ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3073121&h=8cad9246\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3073121</a>"},{"pid":"944c8fbf21e022495b01ab18f481e8668edd1e91","tid":1890871,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:34:47.000Z","msg":"韓亞航空 英文Asiana Airline <br />\n<a href=\"https://flyasiana.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflyasiana.com%2F&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=b329d2e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://flyasiana.com/</a>"},{"pid":"031b62fe43df5a46ea77377d6dba4c745f7a2bb3","tid":1890871,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:09:47.000Z","msg":"韓亞航空 英文Asiana Airline <br />\n<a href=\"https://flyasiana.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflyasiana.com%2F&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVDQMt3kYY